    <item>
      <title>印度即将向印尼出售俄罗斯支持的反舰导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/india-near-sale-of-russia-backed-anti-ship-missiles-to-indonesia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度正考虑向印度尼西亚出售价值 4.5 亿美元的俄罗斯支持的超音速巡航导弹，以加强这个东南亚国家的防御能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/india-near-sale-of-russia-backed-anti-ship-missiles-to-indonesia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称可能从下个月开始对中国征收 10% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-says-he-s-still-weighing-10-tariff-threat-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他威胁对中国所有进口产品征收 10% 的关税的可能性仍然存在，并暗示最早可能在下个月实施。就在前一天，特朗普将世界第二大经济体中国排除在了他即将瞄准的国家之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-says-he-s-still-weighing-10-tariff-threat-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普授权移民局突击搜查教堂和学校以驱逐出境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-offers-immigration-agents-new-freedoms-for-arrests-amid-broad-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统誓言开始大规模驱逐出境并发布命令包括授权移民局进入教堂和学校等先前受到保护的场所后，从纽约到芝加哥和洛杉矶等城市的移民社区仍然处于紧张状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-offers-immigration-agents-new-freedoms-for-arrests-amid-broad-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 23:16:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普力推美国成为人工智能超级大国，减少护栏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-pushes-to-make-us-an-ai-superpower-with-fewer-guardrails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新政府鼓励加大投资，减少对安全和气候问题的关注。]]></description>
